{"word":"G3193 - μελίσσιος - melíssios - mel-is'-see-os - Honeycomb","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μελίσσιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">melíssios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">mel-is'-see-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Honeycomb</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தேன்கூடு - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"of bees, made by bees"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3192 - μέλι - méli - mel'-ee/3192\">G3192</a>; <i>relating to honey</i>, that is, <i>bee</i> (comb): - honeycomb.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}